title: Tacoholics
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Fast food, Mexican, European, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A cozy Tex-Mex and coffee place offers typical Tex-Mex-food such as tacos, quesadillas, and wraps. Menu is meat-free besides chicken, and everything can be altered upon request. Staff is well-informed about veganism. Has soy, rice and oat milks for coffee. Free Wi-Fi.
